---
title: Mexican Chorizo, Bean Chilli & Tomato Salsa with Garlic Rice & Coriander
description: Say hello to the best bean in town, nutrient-packed black beans and cmild chorizo. They are wholesome and filling and go perfectly in a bowl with garlic rice and a tomato-cucumber salsa. Now cook it up in a fiery sauce to drive home those mouth-watering flavours.
